import { useRef } from 'react'; import './index.css' import axios from 'axios'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router'; const SignUp =()=>{ const username:any = useRef(); const email:any = useRef(); const password:any = useRef(); const passwordAgain:any = useRef() const redirect = useNavigate(); const handleRegister=async()=>{ try{ const User = { username: username.current.value, email: email.current.value, password: password.current.value, } if(password.current.value == passwordAgain.current.value){ const newUser = await axios.post(`http://localhost:3333/signup`,User) redirect('/login') } else{ passwordAgain.current.setCustomValidity("Password don't match... Please try again...") } } catch(err){ console.log(err) } } return<> /*

Create a new account

Forgot your password?
*/} } export default SignUp
